# Vendored test fixtures and R-derived goldens are byte-exact blobs pinned by
# test/fixtures.lock.json (sha256). Disable end-of-line conversion so a fresh
# checkout matches the lock on every platform — some contributors have
# core.autocrlf=input, which strips CR on commit and would break the sha256 check
# for the CSVs that legitimately contain CRLF. `-text` keeps them diffable.
test/fixtures/** -text
test/golden/** -text
